---
layout: base.njk
title: Our Cats
description: Six cats, every major condition, and the full story of how Paws Over Odds came to exist.
pageClass: our-cats
---

<div class="page-hero page-hero--forest">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">The ones who made this</div>
    <h1>Six cats. A lifetime of <em>lessons.</em></h1>
    <p>Every condition covered on this site was lived through by one of these cats. This is their story — and the reason this resource exists.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="cats-section">
  <div class="cats-inner">
    <div class="cats-timeline">

      {% for cat in cats %}
      <div class="cat-entry cat-{{ cat.status }}" id="{{ cat.slug }}">

        <div class="cat-photo-col">
          <img src="{{ cat.photo | url }}" alt="{{ cat.name }}" class="cat-photo" loading="lazy">
          <span class="cat-status-badge badge-{{ cat.status }}">
            {% if cat.status == 'living' %}Living with CKD{% else %}In memory{% endif %}
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="cat-body">
          <div class="cat-role">{{ cat.role }}</div>
          <h2 class="cat-name">{{ cat.name }}</h2>
          <p class="cat-subtitle">{{ cat.subtitle }}</p>

          <div class="cat-tags">
            {% for condition in cat.conditions %}
            <span class="cat-tag tag-{{ condition.type }}">{{ condition.label }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>

          <div class="cat-story">
            {% for paragraph in cat.story %}
            <p>{{ paragraph }}</p>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>

          <blockquote class="cat-lesson">
            <strong>What {{ cat.name }} taught us</strong>
            {{ cat.lesson }}
          </blockquote>
        </div>

      </div>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cats-cta">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <h2>Their stories are why this resource exists.</h2>
    <p>If you're here because your cat is sick, you're in the right place. Start with the condition that brought you here.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="{{ '/conditions/' | url }}" class="btn btn-primary">Browse All Conditions</a>
      <a href="{{ '/advocate/' | url }}" class="btn btn-outline">Vet Advocacy Toolkit</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
